Critic: person who makes reviews
Review: rank given to a film by a critic
Director: person who make a film alone or with other directors
Film: Picture made by one or several directors and reviewed by one or several critics
Direction: attribution of directors for each film

Critics
- ID
- First Name
- Last Name
- Company
- Nationality

Directors
- ID
- First Name
- Last Name
- Nationality

Films
- ID
- Release date
- Title                 
- Budget
- Incomes

Reviews
- ID
- Critic ID
- Film ID
- Rank

Directions
- Film ID
- Director ID

Countries
- Common name
- Code
